data.description: Why wait when you can have this solid, complete, ready for immediate move-in, already established, quiet, clean and quaint community of Marbella at Davenport! Another fabulous perk: NO CDD, LOW HOA and the flexibility of primary residence or SHORT TERM RENTAL!! A beautiful and exceptionally well kept 3 bedroom, 2 bath Bartley Flex by Royal Oak Builders. This one-owner home features large windows providing plenty of natural light and a charming split floor plan. The owner’s en-suite is on one side and the remaining bedrooms are on the other side providing privacy. The entryway is a stunning gallery-style hallway with a cozy bonus room on the right. Down the hallway, two identical bedrooms with roomy closets share a full bath with double sinks and shower/tub combo. The extra large laundry room is directly across the hallway for convenience. At the end of the gallery style hallway, the home opens to a comfortable living room and dining room combo. The kitchen features newer appliances, plenty of cabinet space, and pendant lighting over the island. The living/dining room and open kitchen are perfect for entertaining. The sizable, private and primary en-suite is tucked away providing tranquility, especially the primary bath featuring double sinks, a relaxing soaker tub, stand alone shower and separate water closet. Off the primary bath, step into the walk-in closet with plenty of space to customize. A two car garage and spacious backyard outdoor living with a gorgeous shaded maple tree adds to all the goodness this home has to offer. While the property is COMPLETELY move-in ready, you still have the option to put your own stamp on it inside or outside! Check out some of the COOL virtually staged photos for ideas! Enjoy close proximity to shopping, entertainment, restaurants, Posner Park, Disney, Universal and all things Orlando. Utilize this home as a primary residence, second home or investment property for short/long term rental. Schedule your showing today!
